            {
              "type": "heading2",
              "text": "Where Work Becomes Wellbeing",
              "spans": []
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "text": "The MHG Headquarters was envisioned as more than a workplace — it was designed as an emotional journey. I led the project from concept to completion, shaping the headquarters around the philosophy of Breath Out, Breath In, Innovation. Each zone was crafted to influence mood, wellbeing, and creativity, turning the office into a living ecosystem of energy and belonging.",
              "spans": []
            }
          ]
